commitResults.messageTitle: Change Duke class to chatBot class; Change output message to skeletal version of greetings and bot name
Modified code to echo commands, exits when user says bye and also included a try again message when none of the correct commands are given.
Modified chatBot to allow adding of Task and showing the list; added Task.java to store task info
Modified ChatBot.java to check for mark and unmark commands; Added instructions to Task.java to include mark and unmark
Rename unmarkDone function to unmarkedDone for both Chatbot.java and Task.java
Reorganised the mark and unmark into functions for easier referencing, Added missing line in list message in ChatBot.java

Added Deadline.java, Event.java, ToDo.java which are extensions of Task.java; updated ChatBot.java to include the 3 new types of Tasks; updated runtest.bat to take ChatBot class when running; updated input.txt and EXPECTED.TXT to check if test cases are correct.
